491
00:24:49,243 --> 00:24:53,284
Sometimes what we'll do to de-risk is we'll create what we call strike teams.

492
00:24:53,284 --> 00:24:56,045
So our strike teams are composed of, you know, many people.

493
00:24:56,918 --> 00:25:01,419
And sometimes we're going to have multiple people of the same trade trying to de-risk the same problem.

494
00:25:01,419 --> 00:25:06,380
Uh, there, it happened two times. Like, two significant strike teams that we had on Far Cry 4 was for,

495
00:25:06,380 --> 00:25:11,321
uh, the elephant riding was one, because, like, you want to, you want to be able to drive the elephant,

496
00:25:11,321 --> 00:25:15,923
but you still want it to feel like a living animal. This is, this has a huge set of problems of their own.

497
00:25:15,923 --> 00:25:23,104
So this was one of the strike team that we did, and we really tried to shield these people as much as possible,

498
00:25:23,104 --> 00:25:26,525
so they can really blitz on making sure that all these risks are eliminated.

