00:30:01,204 --> 00:30:03,765
Aside from that, I mean the experience is pretty solid.

599
00:30:09,378 --> 00:30:15,480
Now, the last step of a feature is the gold and all-in.

600
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:18,260
So like I said earlier, most of the features

601
00:30:18,260 --> 00:30:19,601
will only make it as far as beta.

602
00:30:19,601 --> 00:30:21,981
The features that we still work on past beta

